<h2>People, Products and Professions (Sammelband)</h2>
<h3>Choosing a Name, Choosing a Language. Fachleute, Firmennamen und Fremdsprachen</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='253'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h3>Allgemeine Angaben</h3>
